data.description: Don't miss this beautiful three bedroom home in Inlet Beach, Florida!This picturesque residence offers spacious living and is perfectly situated in the sought-after Grande Pointe community. With three bedrooms, it's an ideal size for families or those desiring extra space. The open concept layout provides a seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.Not only does this home have a fantastic interior, but it also boasts a fabulous outdoor and porch space to enjoy the Florida sunshine. Plus, the convenient location places you just minutes away from pristine beaches, local attractions and the famous 30A corridor.
